00:54:59.697 --> 00:55:02.466 align:middle line:84%
>> LG: And they get you into an
altered state of consciousness.

00:55:02.466 --> 00:55:03.868 align:middle line:90%
>> EA: Right.

00:55:03.868 --> 00:55:06.203 align:middle line:84%
And I'm convinced, based on
the fact that my meningitis,

00:55:06.203 --> 00:55:09.807 align:middle line:84%
which as I said, by inactivating
my neocortex taking it all

00:55:09.807 --> 00:55:12.877 align:middle line:84%
