richer ultra reality.

00:55:16.480 --> 00:55:19.784 align:middle line:84%
Not stuck in time and
space and here and now.

00:55:19.784 --> 00:55:22.586 align:middle line:84%
I though, well, maybe
hemispheric synchronization

00:55:22.586 --> 00:55:24.822 align:middle line:84%
